=head1 DESCRIPTION

Configuration for data quality validation. Used to select the Rulesets
and Validation Mode to be used in the profile job. When
ValidationConfiguration is null, the profile job will run without data
quality validation.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RulesetArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the ruleset to be validated in the
profile job. The TargetArn of the selected ruleset should be the same
as the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the dataset that is associated
with the profile job.


=head2 ValidationMode => Str

Mode of data quality validation. Default mode is
E<ldquo>CHECK_ALLE<rdquo> which verifies all rules defined in the
selected ruleset.



